@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Admin Views Dashboard

actor Admin
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
participant "Auth Middleware (JWT)" as AUTH
database "Database (Neon)" as DB
participant "Cache Layer (Redis - Optional)" as CACHE

== Open Dashboard ==
Admin -> UI: Open 'Dashboard' page
UI -> API: GET /trl/case (JWT)
UI -> API: GET /trl/researchers (JWT)
UI -> API: GET /trl/assessment (JWT)
UI -> API: GET /trl/ip (JWT)
UI -> API: GET /trl/supportment (JWT)
API -> AUTH: Verify JWT & role=Admin
AUTH --> API: Valid / Invalid

alt Invalid Token
    API --> UI: 401 Unauthorized
    UI --> Admin: Redirect to Login
else Valid
    API -> CACHE: Check dashboard cache
    alt Cache Hit
        CACHE --> API: Return cached data
    else Cache Miss
        API -> DB: Fetch case statistics
        API -> DB: Fetch researchers count
        API -> DB: Fetch assessment summary
        API -> DB: Fetch IP summary
        API -> DB: Fetch supportment summary
        DB --> API: Return aggregated results
        API -> CACHE: Store dashboard data (TTL 60s)
    end
    API --> UI: 200 OK (Dashboard Data)
end

UI --> Admin: Display dashboard widgets
UI --> Admin: Display summary cards
UI --> Admin: Display charts

@enduml